Package com.sanyavertolet.interview.data

Class Data

java.lang.Object
com.sanyavertolet.interview.data.Data
public class Data extends Object
Represents the data associated with a cell in a table-like structure, including the cell's text, its evaluated value, and an optional expression tree for cells containing formulas. The Data class supports recalculating its value based on an expression and marking the cell as erroneous if an evaluation fails.
